### ============================================================================
### CART — /api/v1/cart
### ============================================================================

### Get cart items
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Add item to cart
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cart/add
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ebookVersionId": 1
}

### Remove item from cart
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cart/{{cartItemId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Clear cart
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Sync cart
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cart/sync
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {"ebookVersionId": 1},
  {"ebookVersionId": 2}
]

### Cart checkout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cart/checkout
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ebookVersionIds": [1, 2]
}
